{"type": "article", "id": 32835, "title": "秋天到了，好设计可以“织”出来｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-10-01T00:06:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8289, "name": "针织"}, {"id": 33390, "name": "Mottoform"}, {"id": 33391, "name": "Zilalila"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 22532, "name": "Patricia Urquiola"}, {"id": 33392, "name": "Claire-Anne O’Brien"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 139, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160930161937N40C26XDYM8QphtU.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">进入早秋，你是否已经找出了针织衣物为降温做准备？作为一项拥有悠久历史的手工艺术，它也是不少设计师的灵感来源，满足了人们对于温暖的渴望。这周就让我们看看几款融入针织元素的设计。</p><p>          </p><h3>Pooh Table collection by nendo</h3><p>          </p><p>你能猜出这套由日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 为日本迪士尼设计的 Pooh Table 系列家具分别指的是哪些动画角色吗？这一系列家具均采用保留了天然质感的枫木打造而成，设计灵感则来源于经典动画《小熊维尼》，并在局部用彩色的针织物进行点缀。即便它们并没有直接呈现出角色的形象，通过外形和所选取的代表色还是能够联想到家具指代的究竟是谁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141453s9SmMt6E5kLQCNKu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141454WQ4bXBCJleMgLZwr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141454OnDz79cg2pdJZmUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141454kH8Inj3bKt2Bv5rh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141454TpH2M9cj8BxPeI53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141454c8TFmMvyo0L5aE2p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Loop lamps by Mottoform</h3><p>          </p><p>荷兰的 <a href=\"http://www.mottoform.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mottoform</a> 设计工作室由 Elizabeth Salonen 创立，在这套名为 Loop 的灯具系列中，她尝试将传统的手工艺术与 LED 灯结合在一起，使它兼具功能性和雕塑感。柔软的灯罩由荷兰当地的工匠采用纸绳手工编织而成，Salonen 评论说“就像是为 LED 灯搭建房子一样”。有的时候由于编织过松或者过紧，还会进行数次返工。由于工匠的手法各有差异，没有两个灯会是完全一样的。它们最终的形态由针织图案、LED 灯管的形状以及重力的作用所决定，带给人一种多变而温暖的感觉。这个系列目前仍处于原型阶段，Salonen 正在寻找有兴趣的制作商合作生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930100236Hm4LBisO9FP7Vnwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605134\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930100238z7GiqMl1ctJgIDwf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.458435\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609301002392te6GzAPlHf0QNvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.396088\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930100239Q2WMmeFqf6OnP9RY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.323961\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930100240QxRYUu73CE5lOSD9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504890\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Olann by Claire-Anne O’Brien</h3><p>          </p><p>在爱尔兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.claireanneobrien.com/about\" rel=\"nofollow\">Claire-Anne O’Brien</a> 的 Olann 系列中，长椅、凳子、搁脚凳这几样家具通过编织工艺被赋予了崭新的面貌。O’Brien 的灵感来源于渔业和编织这两项爱尔兰乡村生活中主要的劳动方式，编织的样式则借鉴了钓鱼绳结和柳条筐等为当地织工所熟知的元素。每一件家具都是由一组在家工作的织工共同完成的，O’Brien 希望借此延续爱尔兰这种独特的家庭手工业传统。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930145538zuVglWf78qvOpnkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930145538LyqIYkEdMsbDmc1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930145538rOBjwsMvKW7hCS6i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930145538vMeVFpGwfZbxzIW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930145538XSOTmrwqHpUAeuID.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.036675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>NEST by Zilalila</h3><p>          </p><p>如果你喜欢能让你的身体软软地陷进去的豆袋沙发，不妨试试荷兰针织品牌 <a href=\"http://zilalila.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zilalila</a> 推出的 NEST 系列。NEST 选用来自新西兰的羊毛线，内部由 EPS 泡沫塑料填充，每一件都由与 Zilalila 合作的尼泊尔当地编工手工编织而成，并且标上了序列号。这是它的<a href=\"http://zilalila.com/shop/nest\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 599 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930120752nGHZhRTbo7xuMVvK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665672\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930120752XmGtkU4uj2ZKcrRN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609301207527qrfJSTtyZ5xh4Ob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609301207524HgFaNLk8Gq2Qcuw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016093012075220zm1gX4tGIBLH5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Biknit by Patricia Urquiola</h3><p>          </p><p>西班牙设计师 <a href=\"http://www.patriciaurquiola.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Patricia Urquiola</a> 为意大利家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.moroso.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moroso</a> 设计的这套 <a href=\"http://www.patriciaurquiola.com/design/biknit/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Biknit</a> 休闲躺椅就像是把一截毛衣放大了一样。它的底座由坚固的白蜡木制成，涤纶/PVC 织物围绕着表面经过喷涂的金属框架编结在一起，看上去相当温暖舒适。在房间里放上这么一张躺椅，可以配上柔软的枕头和一本书惬意地度过一个午后。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141043YP7Qg2pKnJo0eBMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.846000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141043meyZP39scQvtdjNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.450000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609301410435CepMUQE7Oxh9YTk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930141043JsLgh36UkcmnSwuV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Coaster set by CRESUS artisanat</h3><p>          </p><p>居住在美国洛杉矶的织物爱好者 Angie Cho 在 Esty 上经营着一家名为 Yumster Friends 的网店，出售她亲手编织的羊毛玩具和小篮子。除了猫咪、熊和兔子这些可爱的动物之外，你还能找到她为了纪念 David Bowie <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/248492784/david-bowie-cat-plush\" rel=\"nofollow\">特别设计的款式</a>。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/YumsterFriends\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些小巧精美的手工织物，售价从 24 到 44 美元不等。如果你对她的设计感兴趣的话，还可以在她的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yumsterfriends/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 上看到更多照片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930165542G1nAzoPEtc62eQKm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930165543aA94l6DX3NO5ZexW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930165543z6h93pDQ5ZLV4dCl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930165542r3MDRK5eNqdVmzOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160930165543FO9XGnyMsDIg1iWk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609301655421mk6wOf08YA5IoqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}